name: end time (memento mori)
description:
This animated flyer is a giveaway to celebrate the final Halloween party (in a long series) thrown at the Snake Pit, a well loved location in Dane County, Wisconsin.

The party will run from 9 PM on October 30th until dawn of Halloween morning.

These were amazing parties and I was very happy to help with some artwork to commemorate the night. I hope that if you are watching this from somewhere else in the world that at least it's an interesting example of one of the few CLIP guided diffusion videos in existence..
